Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounters are mysterious!\NBut cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Conan's 100th episode!\NMy first love is about to be found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Memories of\NFirst Love Case (Part 1)."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for offering to clean\NShinichi's house, Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem!\NWe have nothing to do anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide these things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will turn into a\Nghost house if we don't clean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi must be happy to have\Nsuch a thoughtful girlfriend as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're off, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of cleaning\Nthe entire house, are you, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's do as much\Nas we can for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Does that mean we're\Ngoing to clean all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Sonoko-{\i1}sama {\i0}get stuck\Ncleaning Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on such a nice Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just ignored it,\Nyet you went and got Doc's spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just figured\Nthe place was covered in dust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that it'd be hard to clean alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sonoko. You should dust\Nthe bookcases before sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say, you should\Nclean from the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you're supposed to follow\Nthe tiles when sweeping the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like such an old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls these days are supposed\Nto be crazy about catching men
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and experiencing pure love,\Nfirst love, and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet here I am, getting covered\Nin dust for that mystery dweeb...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm oh-so-pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry for the trouble, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Speaking of first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose\NShinichi's first love was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've had a love or two by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. He's super-dull in the head\Nwhen it comes to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, given his hot mother,\Nit was probably a TV idol, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you've always\Nbeen together since you were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more,\Nyou're thoughtful and strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows,\Nmaybe you're his first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! We only played\Ntogether when we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then there's your precedent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't Shinichi-{\i1}kun {\i0}your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Don't make stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your bashfulness says\Notherwise, Girl of Twenty Faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Sonoko! Before I get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb!\NIt's obviously Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I kind of doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he ring the\Ndoorbell to his own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably heard about us from\Nthe doc and wants to surprise us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Shinichi didn't say\Nanything about coming home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so embarrassed about?\NHurry and see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your first love prince, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Isn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, are you Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was student body president\Nduring our first year of middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! Uchida Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Uchida Asami (18) Toto Univ. Literature Dept., 1st Year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So Kudo-{\i1}kun {\i0}has been\Naway for a while on some cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I always\Ngot the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it's almost like\NI've asked you to clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem at all!\NI had nothing else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}. Why did you\Nwant to see Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends in the university's\Nmystery club are going to rent a lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold a birthday\Nparty for me this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to invite Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as he's a great detective\Nand an old soccer club teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sent the letter quite a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything before he left home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I was sure he would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he forgot about\Nthat confession four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess I can't\Nblame him for forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First loves are bound\Nto fade away with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was Shinichi's first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it. It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was talking about\Nit our first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly a first-year boy\Nmade a pass at Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that daredevil was\Nactually Kudo Shinichi, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that.\NIt was an actual confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shinichi-{\i1}niichan {\i0}won't go,\Nwhy not ask someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've solved a few cases\Nourselves, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We might be able\Nto catch some lively Toto boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think my male friends would\Nlove having high school girls attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you invite us, there's\Nno question that he'll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sonoko! You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The great detective\Nwho needs no introduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A get-together of Toto\NUniversity's mystery study club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow you to go to a\Nsleepover without any real adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're invited too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! I don't have\Ntime to mess with stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As a great detective,\Nyou can't relax on a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for the mystery study club,\NMori Kogoro-{\i1}san {\i0}is almost like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How they'd all like to\Nhear from the peerless detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention all the\Npretty girls who'll be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including Uchida Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0},\Nwho holds the title of Miss Toto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're busy,\Nwe'll accept that we can't go either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure I can somehow\Nrearrange my busy schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go with you as your chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wouldn't want to\Ndisappoint all the promising youngsters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of this mystery study club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my stories about the cases\NI've solved can help them in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it may be my duty as\Na great detective to assist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a predictable personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Toto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus stop is here,\Nso we go up and right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Over there?\NMiss Toto isn't too far now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm gonna get me a Toto boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being able to talk and drink\Nwith the young minds of Toto U.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, you're all\Ngood-looking boys and pretty girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:40.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawai Manabu (22) Literature Dept.,\N 4th Year, President of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd expect from a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to control
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people's hearts with words alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:46.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayasaka Tomoko (21) Literature Dept.,\N4th Year, V.P. of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you sure you're not referring to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playboy Sawai-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made a 1st-year girl cry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:53.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi Shibahisa (20) Literature Dept., 2nd Year \NMiyazaki Chika (19) Literature Dept., 2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just recently, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! This is\NAsami's birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to put me on trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And it's also a celebration party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the "Newcomer Award"\Nher novel won the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too bad, Morimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made it\Nto the final selection, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:17.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Morimoto Yoshinobu (22) Literature Dept., 3rd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Asami-{\i1}kun{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our department's most promising writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to her pair in the Literature\NDepartment's tennis tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus she was named\NMiss Toto as a freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even make it through\Nthe preliminary round...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really admire her. She can do\Neverything, but doesn't act conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also an incredible cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,\Nwhere is her lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Ran are baking it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asami-{\i1}kun {\i0}said she was\Ngoing to make one and bring it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sloppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really make this, Asami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did. It was my first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your pie, Asami-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally forgot to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would make\None for me, so I asked her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Why're you making\Nstuff you don't know how to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Save your criticism\Nuntil after you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little fragrant, but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It looks iffy, but tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? With cooking,\Nsubstance is what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you eat it, you can't tell\Nwhat it looks like anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've solved every\Ncase 100% of the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you solved the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a pretty cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went all the way to Ginza to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find some matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's okay. I borrowed\NSawai-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any age, watching birthday\Ncandles being lit is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, only until you're 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Once you're over 20,\Nyou start to hate each extra candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:57.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations. I pray for even greater future \Nsuccess. Toto Literature Prof. Takamura Masao
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right at midnight, as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's good we got\Na lodge with a fax machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0} sent it, Asami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. What should\Nwe do with the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to go to the\Nkaraoke place by the station next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I already made reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save the cake for tomorrow\Nand go do karaoke ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nothing else\Nwe can do. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:40.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The mystery begins to unravel! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, little boy. Want to sing\NTwo-Mix with me next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the glum look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! I'm not glum at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I guess what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart and beautiful,\Na sports warrior and scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considerate, popular,\Nand ♪1 at everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about\NAsami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How could you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm no match for her!"\Nis written all over your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't blame\NShinichi-{\i1}kun {\i0}for falling for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the soccer club's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about it!\NShe must've rejected him anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Shinichi\Nloves lemon pie, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it for the first time\Ntoday from Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Shinichi loves lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's his favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told everyone I'd make one\Nbecause I thought he'd come today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Shinichi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can teach you how\Nto make it if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows so much\Nabout Shinichi that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, cheer up! You have\Nyour own good qualities too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! You are strong and\Nbrawny 'cause you practice karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There are a lot fewer people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were taking\Nso long in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ran off to the\Nbathrooms by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you have my cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some at the\Nconvenience store next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Noguchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still walking around\Nthe train station to sober up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past 3:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should head back.\NWe left the place messy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tidy up and hit the hay--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Is that a fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Asami-{\i1}senpai {\i0}is still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to the lodge!\NWe might still make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rental car key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi-{\i1}kun {\i0}has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's the problem"?!\NThe lodge we rented is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}... {\i1}Senpai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be all right,\NAsami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! It doesn't look\Nlike she fled outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me she's\Nstill asleep inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we call her on the phone?!\NShe was asleep in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It's already burned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use! There's no way inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Move that motorcycle!\NWe don't want its gasoline to ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fire truck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My helmet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, {\i1}Senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ran and Conan went inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,President Sawai followed them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}! Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! My daughter's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be in danger too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hospital near the lodge.\NThey brought you here afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Asami-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than a little carbon\Nmonoxide poisoning, she's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! She made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NYou're the one who saved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all...\NI rushed inside without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sawai-{\i1}san {\i0}led the way\Nto safety after I found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt relieved when I got outside,\Nbut things got blurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was amazing! You busted\Ninside with that helmet on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the firefighters said that\Nit wasn't smart to go into the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but wearing the helmet\Nwas the correct thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave it to me just as\NI was about to run inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I should put it on to protect\Nmy hair and face from the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}did? He's as\Nstrange a kid as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the fire started around 2:50?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. People in nearby lodges\Nsaid they saw smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought it was a bonfire at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you suspect it was arson?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The fire started in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cake candle was probably the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It probably fell\Nonto the floor while still lit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where it ignited the nearby\Nwrapping paper and curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you blow them out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I did put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.\NWe were all in a hurry when we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the candle did burn down to its base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't forget to put it out,\Nthere's one other possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility that Asami-{\i1}san\N{\i0}herself lit the fire in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd! Why would she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've left while we were\Ngetting something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Dad?!
